Pn

P n-1

p n = p n-1 +1

1 0.5*1

2 0.5*1*0.5 = 0.25

3 0.5*0.5*0.5 = 0.125

0.5*1 + 0.25*2 + 0.125*3 +...+ 0.5^n *n

sn = 1/2^1 + 2/2^2 + 3/2^3 + 4/2^4  + ... + n/2^n

1/2 Sn = 1/2^2 + 2/2^3 + 3/2^4 + ...+ n/2^n+1

相减

1/2 Sn = 1/2 + 1/4 + 1/8 +...+ 1/2^n - n/2^n+1(=0)
       = 1/2 *(1-1/2^n)/(1-1/2)
       = 1/2 * 2
       = 1


so Sn = 2
=> Sn = 2